{"tid":161603,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"學French, Spanish定日文","createTime":"2017-03-18T15:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T15:26:22.000Z","uid":36008,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d298bc2620e1366eefab8da50a35412e999f27ea","tid":161603,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"想學多一種語言 增加自己優勢同競爭力<br />\n以全球應用程度 一定係Spanish 或者 French<br />\n但喺亞洲 會唔會日文好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係我好鍾意睇日文版多啦A夢 睇左幾年 所以興趣大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：讀law 遲啲去Ireland exchange<br />\n邊個語言對未來就業好啲 或者喺愛爾蘭多啲人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麻煩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69db4fe0289d8dc2cd21e39c3e56eef522bedf8","tid":161603,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:00:34.000Z","msg":"學French Spanish&lt;--溝鬼妹<br />\n學日文&lt;--溝架妺"},{"pid":"c6b9e49b412a7a1d51ef672573f2702ad2a66ead","tid":161603,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:03:00.000Z","msg":"Why not all?"},{"pid":"f5188dfa238a36b30418234de8d58c4bc390e805","tid":161603,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"聽講如果識法文 西班牙文會易學好多~"},{"pid":"8064650de7015b6be4e66e4be49a637e968312d5","tid":161603,"uid":48680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:04:26.000Z","msg":"日文就興趣行先架啦,除非諗住做日資/移民 否則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且難度上大過西/法 文<br />\n<br />\n西就拉丁美洲/西班牙/美國多人講<br />\n法就非洲/法國 多人講<br />\n你識西班牙文/法文就好易識埋另一樣<br />\n而且本身識英文已有40%自動識<br />\n<br />\n利申:日文N2,識D 口語西班牙文<br />\n<br />\nTLDR:就業,三個都冇咩用,但西&gt;法&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;日本,愛爾蘭未去過5G"},{"pid":"e4c23a5af0ada27b9bfc73e6ba5f5bf06b4c155c","tid":161603,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"日本語"},{"pid":"89ab44b2bba387964a8a59e497d265a077117db6","tid":161603,"uid":80419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"Spanish 易上手啲 比起 French"},{"pid":"a2d084355c34a87c310e6b7abcb366844777eac6","tid":161603,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:07:15.000Z","msg":"如果係學術人，請讀french，好多經典文獻都係用french寫。英文字有成一半都係originate from french。好多賴係高級既場合/餐廳，都會故意用French。同埋如果去歐洲發展，讀french。<br />\n<br />\n如果想世界各地咁yo人，讀spanish。如果去美國發展，讀spanish。<br />\n<br />\n如果想係亞洲發展，讀日文。<br />\n<br />\n視乎你既career同邊到既經濟活動較多。老實講，好多鬼佬自己都已經識french/spanish，但係佢地識日文既唔知有冇0.01%，所以識日文都有助凸顯你既優勢"},{"pid":"d8e31dda5f6e8065c79c1b8f5bc3cc190a439c8c","tid":161603,"uid":86634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:10:05.000Z","msg":"Law 既French好似幾抵玩"},{"pid":"21236eb539c9fd2e91d1cbc32a45d018e90ca97d","tid":161603,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"既然你都話競爭力，日文根本無考慮嘅理由<br />\n<br />\n西班牙文會實用少少"},{"pid":"2e73da5a72f55b2a0235cd7970583ac940f95d80","tid":161603,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係學術人，請讀french，好多經典文獻都係用french寫。英文字有成一半都係originate from french。好多賴係高級既場合/餐廳，都會故意用French。同埋如果去歐洲發展，讀french。<br />\n<br />\n如果想世界各地咁yo人，讀spanish。如果去美國發展，讀spanish。<br />\n<br />\n如果想係亞洲發展，讀日文。<br />\n<br />\n視乎你既career同邊到既經濟活動較多。老實講，好多鬼佬自己都已經識french/spanish，但係佢地識日文既唔知有冇0.01%，所以識日文都有助凸顯你既優勢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學語言最緊要多練習<br />\n嚟緊去exchange會遊歐<br />\n照你咁講可能French好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c5a6f99b65340d5bc583384a50a425db10209d","tid":161603,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學French Spanish&lt;--溝鬼妹<br />\n學日文&lt;--溝架妺</blockquote><br />\n溝架仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c85c7d8ac87ce5494b40e6a534fc00b0a0c908","tid":161603,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:20:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Spanish 易上手啲 比起 French</blockquote><br />\nFrench啲grammar pronoun難到PK<br />\n但vocab同英文又似 :0"},{"pid":"59cea62da67ab02dfbc6e55b33cf7088e4d73fc4","tid":161603,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"難度：日&gt;法&gt;西<br />\n人數：西&gt;法&gt;日<br />\n好聽：日&gt;法&gt;西<br />\n對英文幫助：法&gt;西&gt;日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得法文無得輸 有接近一半英文係法文傳過去/有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一堆文學巨著都係法文寫： 海底兩萬里 地心探險記 <br />\n<br />\n美女與野獸 80日環遊世界 基督山恩仇記 小王子 異鄉人 <br />\n<br />\n太多太多你可能原本以為係英文作品 其實原著都係法文寫既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b911e3f4ffa17f0192f85997942889d000f9e964","tid":161603,"uid":86634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學French Spanish&lt;--溝鬼妹<br />\n學日文&lt;--溝架妺</blockquote><br />\n溝架仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n㗎仔，不了"},{"pid":"a69b1675cb0799c4d0ed2e4da51f6c3684d19795","tid":161603,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T17:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果係學術人，請讀french，好多經典文獻都係用french寫。英文字有成一半都係originate from french。好多賴係高級既場合/餐廳，都會故意用French。同埋如果去歐洲發展，讀french。<br />\n<br />\n如果想世界各地咁yo人，讀spanish。如果去美國發展，讀spanish。<br />\n<br />\n如果想係亞洲發展，讀日文。<br />\n<br />\n視乎你既career同邊到既經濟活動較多。老實講，好多鬼佬自己都已經識french/spanish，但係佢地識日文既唔知有冇0.01%，所以識日文都有助凸顯你既優勢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學語言最緊要多練習<br />\n嚟緊去exchange會遊歐<br />\n照你咁講可能French好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會揀法文，因為法文真係好grand，個connections又wealthier好多。除非你去美國，唔係的話都係法文好d。<br />\n<br />\n遊歐其實都係french多d人用，起碼Belgium/Switzerland都25%-50%既population係native in french，Netherlands果d小國家，個個都識讀french（中小學課程要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。"},{"pid":"2d6fa45acef1d556821937e063a67335793d567a","tid":161603,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T17:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學French Spanish&lt;--溝鬼妹<br />\n學日文&lt;--溝架妺</blockquote><br />\n溝架仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n㗎仔，不了</blockquote><br />\n東方女性學日文扮架妹更易系西方搵食／上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977eee74d398d4d447bc65fdce64666ce971e40c","tid":161603,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T17:56:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54d71edad22fc14f7d27be10a3b856ce1994291d","tid":161603,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學French Spanish&lt;--溝鬼妹<br />\n學日文&lt;--溝架妺</blockquote><br />\n溝架仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n㗎仔，不了</blockquote><br />\n東方女性學日文扮架妹更易系西方搵食／上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吔咩嗲&gt;&lt;"},{"pid":"2fe5fd9ab97e83dc9899098487f3f214e591959e","tid":161603,"uid":28190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:16:19.000Z","msg":"三種語言都學過，不過依家淨係得返日文有興趣"},{"pid":"1fe30a417e7d915a8f412c35d1af659139c4378a","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:35:47.000Z","msg":"三樣都學<br />\n利申：三樣一齊學緊"},{"pid":"4beb56183e1b088e714e7099060772688e7ed631","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:39:35.000Z","msg":"有冇人評埋德文，意文，俄文？"},{"pid":"2c4f1d1ef03ff2a75881136a57fb9f4add4c72b6","tid":161603,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3DuzBDr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3DuzBDr.gif&h=0755b4d8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f69648f3bcc5bae935bb57f04cf7d6977df64b","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>既然你都話競爭力，日文根本無考慮嘅理由<br />\n<br />\n西班牙文會實用少少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係既, 你去歐洲做野咪有用囉, 法文西文呢D變成好basic個個都有既野<br />\n如果想突出自己之餘讀既文又有用, 可能阿拉伯文係唔錯既選擇, 話晒3億人口又唔係咁多非中東人識, 因為太難"},{"pid":"0115fe6c8e4a05adde9bf57a7e871c99ab56cd24","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學French Spanish&lt;--溝鬼妹<br />\n學日文&lt;--溝架妺</blockquote><br />\n溝鬼妹俄文一定最實用"},{"pid":"0e7bdaba0e8d4967ab110c492608099b715abff8","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學French Spanish&lt;--溝鬼妹<br />\n學日文&lt;--溝架妺</blockquote><br />\n溝鬼妹俄文一定最實用</blockquote><br />\n韓文就用黎溝d後生腦筍都未生埋, 迷緊kpop既十幾歲俄妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571a493f9b06a860f016b15593ba3962479fa5e7","tid":161603,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:53:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好多法語地區只要你識法文就好易移民</span>"},{"pid":"b9dfc2fe84e698f109cd0d2ddbb3cece0f0495bc","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好多法語地區只要你識法文就好易移民</span></blockquote><br />\n而家法國外籍兵團都要識左法文先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff2fdc6853ab3e448251e21bedf41bce272da5e","tid":161603,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好多法語地區只要你識法文就好易移民</span></blockquote><br />\n而家法國外籍兵團都要識左法文先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法語地區唔係指法國<br />\n你了解下加拿大既法語地區<br />\n今年又開放2000個名額"},{"pid":"82b2ff0e7e21dd164e36c1c8bb1b03184b14ad6c","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好多法語地區只要你識法文就好易移民</span></blockquote><br />\n而家法國外籍兵團都要識左法文先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法語地區唔係指法國<br />\n你了解下加拿大既法語地區<br />\n今年又開放2000個名額</blockquote><br />\n我知呀, 我唔係反駁緊你, 反而係support緊你, 指french既prerequisite對法語地區好重要<br />\n反而德國唔太care你本身識唔識"},{"pid":"bf0e08d17ca91551b06f464c1cd7661dd6097bd9","tid":161603,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好多法語地區只要你識法文就好易移民</span></blockquote><br />\n而家法國外籍兵團都要識左法文先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法語地區唔係指法國<br />\n你了解下加拿大既法語地區<br />\n今年又開放2000個名額</blockquote><br />\n我知呀, 我唔係反駁緊你, 反而係support緊你, 指french既prerequisite對法語地區好重要<br />\n反而德國唔太care你本身識唔識</blockquote><br />\n呢個我agger 去德國留學<br />\n佢會免費俾你讀一年German course for complete beginner"},{"pid":"8337662f45343563b5edc99516c4675a9e937bc1","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好多法語地區只要你識法文就好易移民</span></blockquote><br />\n而家法國外籍兵團都要識左法文先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法語地區唔係指法國<br />\n你了解下加拿大既法語地區<br />\n今年又開放2000個名額</blockquote><br />\n我知呀, 我唔係反駁緊你, 反而係support緊你, 指french既prerequisite對法語地區好重要<br />\n反而德國唔太care你本身識唔識</blockquote><br />\n呢個我agger 去德國留學<br />\n佢會免費俾你讀一年German course for complete beginner</blockquote><br />\n我知英文program係會逼你讀德文（呢樣好正常）<br />\n不過德文program好似都要你DSH全1/TestDaF全3先會放個conditional offer畀你入去讀德文？<br />\n不過我講緊既係已經畀你讀degree，但你一年內meet唔到德文要求就踢出去<br />\n如果本身零德文知識我就唔知點<br />\n我係講緊德國對唔識德文既人社會接受度高啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算俄羅斯你去讀書都會畀你讀一年俄文預科，不過我相信冇乜人會話俄羅斯對唔識俄文既外國人接受度高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7870260794e67fc2bc0c937b87a7b2abd3982803","tid":161603,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"法國人對法文既要求，好明顯比德國人 strict好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個歐洲得2個國家個education system，係唔洗強制學生讀其他歐洲語言，一係英國，一個係法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354667358d912b320ebcfdd45a178c859d8879bb","tid":161603,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日文就興趣行先架啦,除非諗住做日資/移民 否則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且難度上大過西/法 文<br />\n<br />\n西就拉丁美洲/西班牙/美國多人講<br />\n法就非洲/法國 多人講<br />\n你識西班牙文/法文就好易識埋另一樣<br />\n而且本身識英文已有40%自動識<br />\n<br />\n利申:日文N2,識D 口語西班牙文<br />\n<br />\nTLDR:就業,三個都冇咩用,但西&gt;法&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;日本,愛爾蘭未去過5G</blockquote><br />\n讀法文易過日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4c8b2e9cf793383051eefb0d57a6debdcdcaca","tid":161603,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法國人對法文既要求，好明顯比德國人 strict好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個歐洲得2個國家個education system，係唔洗強制學生讀其他歐洲語言，一係英國，一個係法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英文法文都係強勢語言"},{"pid":"160ecfd775563beff8b6454a19a8dc64813481e0","tid":161603,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日文就興趣行先架啦,除非諗住做日資/移民 否則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且難度上大過西/法 文<br />\n<br />\n西就拉丁美洲/西班牙/美國多人講<br />\n法就非洲/法國 多人講<br />\n你識西班牙文/法文就好易識埋另一樣<br />\n而且本身識英文已有40%自動識<br />\n<br />\n利申:日文N2,識D 口語西班牙文<br />\n<br />\nTLDR:就業,三個都冇咩用,但西&gt;法&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;日本,愛爾蘭未去過5G</blockquote><br />\n讀法文易過日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日文應該係公認最難語言之一<br />\n<br />\n但對用開中文既人<br />\n<br />\n比較容易上手睇得明<br />\n<br />\n但難精囉<br />\n<br />\n法文對我地反而會更難入手"},{"pid":"2856f8fe946d721ab99431b6ee5ae9fcf783c6ed","tid":161603,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:07:49.000Z","msg":"法文比較有用<br />\n去聯合國/歐盟做intern，法文同英文係必須，因爲UN官方語言係英文同發文，德文/西班牙文都只係當第三語言"},{"pid":"3839099e931ad2ce9690b296b8b4d3c3944f594c","tid":161603,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:20:44.000Z","msg":"美國好多Hispanic 講西班牙文<br />\n侵侵最唔鍾意嘅墨西哥人<br />\n但其實幾有用<br />\n<br />\n好多法語國家都好窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以覺得西班牙文會有用啲<br />\n<br />\n利申 je parle francais"},{"pid":"d6a918211231b0245d13edba4fa1e3b2bc826814","tid":161603,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s45zcu3f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs45zcu3f&h=b275bc00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLet data speaks<br />\n<br />\nCentrality: (多唔多其他語言係&quot;centred on&quot;/ related to 呢隻語言) <br />\nFrench ~&gt; German &gt;&gt; Spanish &gt;&gt; Japanese<br />\n原因：好撚多語言源自係法文德文，所以佢地同其他文既connectivity較高，e.g. Swedish/dutch from german, english from french<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTranslations from :（有幾多文獻係translated from呢隻語言。roughly當做隻語言貢獻左幾多原文文獻） <br />\nFrench ~&gt; German &gt;&gt; Spanish &gt;&gt; Japanese<br />\n原因：有好撚多以法德為原文寫成的文獻，源於佢地早期到二十世紀中既強大影響力<br />\n<br />\nTranslations to: (有幾多文獻係translated to 呢隻語言)<br />\nGerman &gt; French ~&gt; Spanish &gt;&gt; Japanese<br />\n原因：唔知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNumber of Speakers :<br />\nSpanish &gt;&gt; French ~&gt; German &gt;&gt; Japanese<br />\n原因:成個南美同美國都極多人講spanish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日文冇咩人當做second languages，except asians<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGDP per capita : (講呢隻語言既人平均幾有錢)<br />\nGerman &gt; Japanese &gt;&gt; Spanish &gt;&gt; French<br />\n原因：法國、西班牙、同南美等地經濟唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddddb47fae5e4ce6f975b63394b6c8db8edd860","tid":161603,"uid":91304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人評埋德文，意文，俄文？</blockquote><br />\n義大利文除左有特定需要（工作上ex同義大利人做生意，溝女，興趣），我會話嘥9氣<br />\n利申 parlo italiano ma non bene <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442e973e849534486dc5abaaafac42eeb3a4c801","tid":161603,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTranslations to: (有幾多文獻係translated to 呢隻語言)<br />\nGerman &gt; French ~&gt; Spanish &gt;&gt; Japanese<br />\n原因：唔知<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n德國有大規模翻譯英美學術文獻既習慣<br />\n他們cite journal多數都會cite一個認受性高既德譯本，即使多數德國人英文都好好"},{"pid":"5d4673da8035d01035819dc45f6b7118495d2909","tid":161603,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法文比較有用<br />\n去聯合國/歐盟做intern，法文同英文係必須，因爲UN官方語言係英文同發文，德文/西班牙文都只係當第三語言</blockquote><br />\n我都係見到French係UN嘅official language<br />\n即刻想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239496fa148bbad2e8877f8762422f1e104fd6cd","tid":161603,"uid":21431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:44:15.000Z","msg":"德文 Ich liebe Deustch <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae46da7d79ca2fd185429a825d1be9e402381359","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法文比較有用<br />\n去聯合國/歐盟做intern，法文同英文係必須，因爲UN官方語言係英文同發文，德文/西班牙文都只係當第三語言</blockquote><br />\nSpanish都係UN官方語言黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242441a5add7b72aa37f55dd3acb2a6f122b7d46","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法文比較有用<br />\n去聯合國/歐盟做intern，法文同英文係必須，因爲UN官方語言係英文同發文，德文/西班牙文都只係當第三語言</blockquote><br />\nSpanish都係UN官方語言黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德文真係慘，70年前戰敗左，就算德國而家經濟雄霸歐盟，都做唔到UN官方語言"},{"pid":"6afbf0f25b1048e1bd207083080e1ff56465cc62","tid":161603,"uid":34782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法國人對法文既要求，好明顯比德國人 strict好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個歐洲得2個國家個education system，係唔洗強制學生讀其他歐洲語言，一係英國，一個係法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法國人唔使學英文架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心唔知"},{"pid":"aec34add5ee1ab9956bfcb71dd494e825e0f1590","tid":161603,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法國人對法文既要求，好明顯比德國人 strict好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個歐洲得2個國家個education system，係唔洗強制學生讀其他歐洲語言，一係英國，一個係法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n法國人唔使學英文架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係compulsory，可以揀唔學英文，雖然好多人都會揀英文黎學"},{"pid":"8490ded670c8cfe3908bf5214320506cd7be2065","tid":161603,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:58:31.000Z","msg":"想學日,德文既PM我<br />\n私人教緊<br />\n<br />\nTG: @abcccccccc"},{"pid":"a9d2f877d57ba339dccb072c0cdef3faec89e01a","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學日,德文既PM我<br />\n私人教緊<br />\n<br />\nTG: @abcccccccc</blockquote><br />\n又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab69fa7294f0cf2328c72eabaeac5818d8eb9865","tid":161603,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法文比較有用<br />\n去聯合國/歐盟做intern，法文同英文係必須，因爲UN官方語言係英文同發文，德文/西班牙文都只係當第三語言</blockquote><br />\nSpanish都係UN官方語言黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nspanish, russian同中文都係<br />\n但多數國際組織既language requirement都係fluent English + fluent French + third languages，最起碼我問係eu parliament同UN做過既同學，都係識英文同法文<br />\n原因應該係多數國際性合同/國際法都係由法文寫，我讀國際私法(conflicts of law)個時都幾多法文詞彙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a190fbad8e0757824acfe255238291db7ced88e6","tid":161603,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>法文比較有用<br />\n去聯合國/歐盟做intern，法文同英文係必須，因爲UN官方語言係英文同發文，德文/西班牙文都只係當第三語言</blockquote><br />\nSpanish都係UN官方語言黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nspanish, russian同中文都係<br />\n但多數國際組織既language requirement都係fluent English + fluent French + other languages，最起碼我問係eu parliament同UN做過既同學，都係識英文同法文<br />\n原因應該係多數國際性合同/國際法都係由法文寫，我讀國際私法(conflicts of law)個時都幾多法文詞彙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"90706f6a3f58e619ffdb4f897c718bb80a969786","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>法文比較有用<br />\n去聯合國/歐盟做intern，法文同英文係必須，因爲UN官方語言係英文同發文，德文/西班牙文都只係當第三語言</blockquote><br />\nSpanish都係UN官方語言黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nspanish, russian同中文都係<br />\n但多數國際組織既language requirement都係fluent English + fluent French + other languages，最起碼我問係eu parliament同UN做過既同學，都係識英文同法文<br />\n原因應該係多數國際性合同/國際法都係由法文寫，我讀國際私法(conflicts of law)個時都幾多法文詞彙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n你都讀過幾多野，本身咩major <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e40803c44bd999b6754e63b2275e7871a7e4f0e","tid":161603,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"德文是咪好難"},{"pid":"e36fde6b1571cb61d52a6d40fd86634ddc786093","tid":161603,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:39:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德文是咪好難</blockquote><br />\n好撚難 4個格既變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43885a611649a3afa51f8fd1ca6aefab3ab45b9d","tid":161603,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>德文是咪好難</blockquote><br />\n好撚難 4個格既變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好處係動詞容易過法西文 但其他都難過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5377ff25639f1b9fb7d5e9947c3fe1d56ed0d610","tid":161603,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:43:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>德文是咪好難</blockquote><br />\n好撚難 4個格既變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好處係動詞容易過法西文 但其他都難過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學返日本鬼子話算"},{"pid":"2e08091059d25a59c77d8cfe7909a6d17c7553be","tid":161603,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>德文是咪好難</blockquote><br />\n好撚難 4個格既變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好處係動詞容易過法西文 但其他都難過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學返日本鬼子話算</blockquote><br />\n日文動詞咪又係多嘢記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff3f42edb4216b41867978f986bb9a55f9974d7","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>德文是咪好難</blockquote><br />\n好撚難 4個格既變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n區區四個格, 仲要除左plural冇乜重大詞尾變化, 輕鬆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0b3a1bc76bf46890896574e78082d8f47c1380","tid":161603,"uid":91304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"其實冇話乜野會易學，扔你係嗰邊生活焗住點都要講又日日睇到咪最易學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （如果你有心學）"},{"pid":"ec4b9c6f58dd06f0535ac9cbc1f54a6a4f7a16e5","tid":161603,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人都話要學德文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現代英語黎講你識法文就自然學埋英文<br />\n英文吸收左好多法文係入面<br />\n法文亦用返好多英文<br />\n好多科學詞彙，日常生活都係法文加英文<br />\n識英法可以話全世界通行<br />\n<br />\n反而德文除左德國同附近國家冇幾多人講"},{"pid":"d373844f84a937c701ad6f2716ae25b345c51b5a","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解咁多人都話要學德文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現代英語黎講你識法文就自然學埋英文<br />\n英文吸收左好多法文係入面<br />\n法文亦用返好多英文<br />\n好多科學詞彙，日常生活都係法文加英文<br />\n識英法可以話全世界通行<br />\n<br />\n反而德文除左德國同附近國家冇幾多人講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 科學詞彙都有唔少德文<br />\n2. 德文雖然地區上比較局限, 但講既國家高質同經濟好, 歐盟龍頭, 係歐洲第一多人講既母語<br />\n3. 德國相對易去讀書, 移民, 搵野做<br />\n4. 世界10%既書係用德文, 有大量既文獻同哲學等名著係用德文寫, 想睇返相對論同量子力學既原文paper都要睇德文"},{"pid":"f9e3de013928d9f81b4da4acd5dd4ff98be794f4","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解咁多人都話要學德文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現代英語黎講你識法文就自然學埋英文<br />\n英文吸收左好多法文係入面<br />\n法文亦用返好多英文<br />\n好多科學詞彙，日常生活都係法文加英文<br />\n識英法可以話全世界通行<br />\n<br />\n反而德文除左德國同附近國家冇幾多人講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 科學詞彙都有唔少德文<br />\n2. 德文雖然地區上比較局限, 但講既國家高質同經濟好, 歐盟龍頭, 係歐洲第一多人講既母語<br />\n3. 德國相對易去讀書, 移民, 搵野做<br />\n4. 世界10%既書係用德文, 有大量既文獻同哲學等名著係用德文寫, 想睇返相對論同量子力學既原文paper都要睇德文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文冇得計, 但講法文既, 除左法國加拿大都冇幾多個真係高質國家, 多數係窮撚國 (講經濟法國自己都唔好得去邊), 但相反講德文既德國奧地利瑞士都相當富裕<br />\n有時唔係睇通唔通行, 多唔多人講, 唔計英文, 講通行直接去西班牙文, 講多人識中文咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0bd677555aa5fc9e9a22891e5edd22fef11daa","tid":161603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解咁多人都話要學德文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現代英語黎講你識法文就自然學埋英文<br />\n英文吸收左好多法文係入面<br />\n法文亦用返好多英文<br />\n好多科學詞彙，日常生活都係法文加英文<br />\n識英法可以話全世界通行<br />\n<br />\n反而德文除左德國同附近國家冇幾多人講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 科學詞彙都有唔少德文<br />\n2. 德文雖然地區上比較局限, 但講既國家高質同經濟好, 歐盟龍頭, 係歐洲第一多人講既母語<br />\n3. 德國相對易去讀書, 移民, 搵野做<br />\n4. 世界10%既書係用德文, 有大量既文獻同哲學等名著係用德文寫, 想睇返相對論同量子力學既原文paper都要睇德文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文冇得計, 但講法文既, 除左法國加拿大都冇幾多個真係高質國家, 多數係窮撚國 (講經濟法國自己都唔好得去邊), 但相反講德文既德國奧地利瑞士都相當富裕<br />\n有時唔係睇通唔通行, 多唔多人講, 唔計英文, 講通行直接去西班牙文, 講多人識中文咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而且識德文係可以通行埋捷克, 荷蘭(雖然呢個英文都得)<br />\n甚至德文係東歐分分鐘多人識過英文, 俄羅斯, 烏克蘭, 波蘭好多學生係學校學德文, 蘇聯以前要輸入德國科技, 同東德又有密切關係, 學德文既傳統去到今時今日<br />\n反而英文又冇乜特別歷史原因令佢地學"},{"pid":"a1c6a960fadbfb44e52faff6958957c69fb6667d","tid":161603,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解咁多人都話要學德文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現代英語黎講你識法文就自然學埋英文<br />\n英文吸收左好多法文係入面<br />\n法文亦用返好多英文<br />\n好多科學詞彙，日常生活都係法文加英文<br />\n識英法可以話全世界通行<br />\n<br />\n反而德文除左德國同附近國家冇幾多人講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 科學詞彙都有唔少德文<br />\n2. 德文雖然地區上比較局限, 但講既國家高質同經濟好, 歐盟龍頭, 係歐洲第一多人講既母語<br />\n3. 德國相對易去讀書, 移民, 搵野做<br />\n4. 世界10%既書係用德文, 有大量既文獻同哲學等名著係用德文寫, 想睇返相對論同量子力學既原文paper都要睇德文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文冇得計, 但講法文既, 除左法國加拿大都冇幾多個真係高質國家, 多數係窮撚國 (講經濟法國自己都唔好得去邊), 但相反講德文既德國奧地利瑞士都相當富裕<br />\n有時唔係睇通唔通行, 多唔多人講, 唔計英文, 講通行直接去西班牙文, 講多人識中文咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多年前學過幾個月法文話就話多人用，但有一半都係非洲窮國，根本唔會去當地應用<br />\n法國人都無乜兩句傾得埋，自大到死，成日逼人認同佢哋諗嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902a37f8fee1d89ca7679c7df6e259f5a09be5d4","tid":161603,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T21:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解咁多人都話要學德文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現代英語黎講你識法文就自然學埋英文<br />\n英文吸收左好多法文係入面<br />\n法文亦用返好多英文<br />\n好多科學詞彙，日常生活都係法文加英文<br />\n識英法可以話全世界通行<br />\n<br />\n反而德文除左德國同附近國家冇幾多人講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 科學詞彙都有唔少德文<br />\n2. 德文雖然地區上比較局限, 但講既國家高質同經濟好, 歐盟龍頭, 係歐洲第一多人講既母語<br />\n3. 德國相對易去讀書, 移民, 搵野做<br />\n4. 世界10%既書係用德文, 有大量既文獻同哲學等名著係用德文寫, 想睇返相對論同量子力學既原文paper都要睇德文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英文冇得計, 但講法文既, 除左法國加拿大都冇幾多個真係高質國家, 多數係窮撚國 (講經濟法國自己都唔好得去邊), 但相反講德文既德國奧地利瑞士都相當富裕<br />\n有時唔係睇通唔通行, 多唔多人講, 唔計英文, 講通行直接去西班牙文, 講多人識中文咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=